{
  "stem": "24195.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I want to continue with the life in the camp and the day that there was an air-- the bomber formations, US bomber formation, had flown over the camp and had attacked Magdeburg.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we heard some-- later, during the day, on the return flight to the-- to France or to England, that we heard that one of the planes had-- motor problems, engine problems, and was coming down.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But it actually landed on-- on the-- on the runway, which was perfect.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a perfect fit-- on one the-- one of the runways.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was a silver-looking Mustang, a fighter plane-- long-range fighter-- US fighter plane.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we didn't-- we only learned later that the pilot was-- was you know, captured, surrendered to the German Air Force personnel there.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we did not see the pilot.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But we were [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was something really totally unexpected and unthinkable, really, for people in Germany, that the pilot was black-- had been black.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It must have been-- it must have been one-- one of those people from that-- this black division of pilots.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They just had a movie about them recently, I think.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I can't think.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They-- have a-- there's still some of these veterans livin'.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that-- that really must-- must have made quite an impression on the Germans.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They didn't expect to find a black pilot there for you know--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well when we heard it, we were all laughing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I know that in the German way of thinkin', that would be-- you know, they-- they would be considered as bad as Jews, or worse.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, they would be called [GERMAN] because they-- they are-- you know, they're just not-- the racist--",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN] ?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[GERMAN] were subhumans.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
